## ğŸ§  Hinglish Explanation

> ğŸ”¸ `String` ek **immutable object** hai. Jab bhi usme kuch change karte ho (jaise add ya replace), ek **naya object** ban jaata hai.

> ğŸ”¹ `StringBuilder` ek **mutable object** hai, jo ek hi object me changes allow karta hai. Isliye **performance ke liye best** hai jab aapko string ko baar-baar change karna ho.

